    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I'm also hearing a lot of conflicting stuff from people in town. Some say it's a moral necessity for the workers, while others say it'll just force local shops to close down. Do you think one of those views is more grounded in economic reality than the other?",
