      "content": "A balanced perspective focuses on the idea of \"living wage\" versus \"business viability.\" Instead of a simple either/or, consider the long-term economic health of the community. A higher wage can lead to a more stable, healthier local workforce, which is good for the town's overall economy. The goal is to find a sustainable wage level that supports employees without creating an unsustainable cost structure for local businesses.",
